@startuml
skinparam monochrome true
skinparam defaultFontSize 11
[*] --> Created
Created --> OnHold : process
OnHold --> Processing : cancel
Processing --> Archived : confirm
Processing : entry / log patient
Archived --> Rejected : update
Rejected --> Draft : confirm
Rejected : entry / log patient
Processing --> Created : revert
Draft --> [*]
@enduml